item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“eshay lad, post:3, topic:393961”]yeah ik where the command list is an that i just need help with liek what is the ::bank ::xteletome or ::givemod command tex just say

if (playerCommand.startsWith(“unban”) && c.playerRights >= 3) {
so on so on**************************************?
like whats the command tex! so i can add the commands to my server but thanks for the help but still if someone could help plz do!!!
thanks![/quote]

No one is going to spoonfeed you. Most of the communities I visit actually put a moderation on users who spoonfeed (and I think it should happen here as well).

How about you write down the steps that would logically be taken for each command until you have a clear and concise understanding of what should happen. Then, find out how to do each of those steps with the code at your disposal. Everything after that will be obvious.
